===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|payen||lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|paier||lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|ML.}} ''[[pacare|pācāre]]'' "to settle, satisfy" from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|paco|pacare|lang=la|to pacify}}. Displaced native {{enm}} {{term|yelden|yelden, yielden|to pay|lang=enm}} (from {{ang}} {{term|gieldan|ġieldan|to pay|lang=ang}}), {{enm}} {{term|scotten|schotten|to pay, make payment|lang=enm}} (from {{ang}} {{term|gescot|scot, ġescot|payment|lang=ang}}).

